features: Exceptional quality: only top-quality materials are used for the production of Japanese natural diapers. Therefore, the cases of diaper rash or dermatitis are especially rare even through the babys skin is sensitive. An exceptional feature of Japanese nappies - they have no chemical odor which becomes especially pungent when diapers are full!

Closer to nature: Moony organic diapers are manufactured using only ecologically clean and safe materials. The materials that come into contact with the skin are made with a weak acidic sheet that contains worry-free, additive-free ingredients (petroleum, fragrance, latex, and synthetic coloring) are made without any additives. Natural Moony Includes 3 types of plant-derived oils: olive oil, jojoba oil, and rice oil.

Soft, fluffy and breathing: the fabric of the internal layer felted from extremely thin fibers is very soft, fluffy and absorbs liquid quickly. Therefore, the babys bum stays dry. Soft and stretchy material, high waist that fits around the belly eliminates the need to worry about slipping or leaking. No fears for leaks due to wide snug-fit gather!

Worry-free all night: even the baby with high body temperature and tends to be sweating a lot, this diaper can keep their bottom dry. 3 notification strips allow you to check the diapers wetness without having to undo any extra buttons. Your babys delicate skin is not capable enough to preserve moisture that is why proper skincare is vital to protecting your babys skin.

Clean-up is simple: It is easy to remove without getting your hands dirty, just lay the baby down and rip the stitches on the side. Then roll up a diaper with the dirty surface inside, and use the tape in the back to fasten. Organic Moony nappies come in a bundle with Americas Toys branded wipes.
body.description: Natural Moony is safe even on newborn skin! Natural Moony, Japans first diaper with a surface sheet made with organic cotton Use 5 different design techniques to make it more gentle for your babys skin. FEATURES: NEW TECHNOLOGY! Full-coverage high waist design! They match exactly the babys inner thighs so there is no gap for leaks even with active babies! NEW TECHNOLOGY! Just roll up the rompers! 3 notification strips allow you to check the diapers wetness without having to undo any extra buttons. NEW TECHNOLOGY! Includes 3 types of plant-derived oils: olive oil, jojoba oil, and rice oil. Also made with materials that are gentle on your babys delicate skin. NEW TECHNOLOGY! Catches runny stool that could irritate your babys skin by using an unevenly-textured absorption zone! It absorbs quickly and away from the skin. Super absorbent, highly breathable and ultra-soft so your active baby stays dry and comfortable! Instantly draws in and locks away pee, leaving the diaper surface drier for longer usage! Stays dry with leak prevention. Even the babies with high body temperature and tends to be sweating a lot, this diaper can keep their bottom dry! Clean-up is simple with the roll-up tape. Roll up a diaper with the dirty surface inside, and use the tape in the back to fasten. The notice indicator line will change into bluish green color, so you can know when to change diaper. Does not stick to your babys skin so your baby stays dry and comfortable. Fit snugly in all positions, stretch gently around your babys waist. No red marks or abrasions at the crotch area!

reviews.reviewText: Incredible diapers, but the NB size is too big for a new born unless your baby is 9 lbs. we started using the NB size diaper once our baby hit 9 lbs, before then, they were too large. But, the diaper is incredibly soft and our baby has not had any rashes or redness since using. We also have not had any blowouts. Highly recommend!
